[{"Code":"en","Title":"BCA VA Direct","Slug":"draft-bca-va-direct","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ij4-82hjwu-001\"><a id=\"_j5wih1vxvjn6\" display=\"false\"></a></p><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ij7-3y7ej0-002\"><a id=\"_df9ij9biwbs1\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ij8-ku6225-003\"><a id=\"_9j6h54imkhti\" display=\"false\"></a>Glossary</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijb-wqtl7e-004\"><strong>Terms</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijb-6mwyln-005\"><strong>Description</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijb-8sp89c-006\">AM</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijc-c5tcly-007\">Account Manager</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijc-4jwj1a-008\">AD</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijc-1p2762-009\">Admin Dashboard</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijc-44d6kv-010\">MO</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijc-sdsyyh-011\">Merchant Ops</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijc-sazt61-012\">VA</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijc-ouabyu-013\">Virtual Account</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijc-5o744p-014\">PG</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijd-vb3gl9-015\">Payment Gateway</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijd-v3vl2s-016\">Company Code</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijd-q3krnx-017\">5 digit Unique number from BCA for each merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijd-2kbzfs-018\">Sub-company code</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijd-c3u02q-019\">Subcode for each merchant under Xendit company code</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijd-jx8ya3-020\">Fixed Bill</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijd-tswjey-021\">User will pay exact amount of bill</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijd-cxc4u2-022\">No Bill</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ije-r25l07-023\">User will input the amount to pay the bill</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ije-3oehoz-024\"><a id=\"_2gi7499bghtf\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ije-7psv8p-025\"><a id=\"_ejxly55we75x\" display=\"false\"></a>Xendit Stakeholders</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ije-2mv89g-026\"><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ije-4hf5wn-027\"><strong>PIC</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ije-e5eq77-028\"><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijf-5xfnsy-029\">Partnership</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijf-1gdt81-030\"><a><u>Anggis Dinda</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijf-3cj181-031\">Partnership PIC for BCA</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijf-el3p82-032\">VA</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijf-0zh7wj-033\"><a><u>Raditya Reza Ariobimo</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijg-zy5kff-034\">Product Manager (Virtual Account)</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijg-gca1t3-035\"><a id=\"_wtd8yjxdsmzg\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijg-u81u6d-036\"><a id=\"_x5gzec6f0lg\" display=\"false\"></a>Related Documents</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijg-aw955b-037\"><strong>Document name</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijg-x3n9ci-038\"><strong>Description</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijg-jv9x00-039\"><strong>Link to document</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijh-0jrkth-040\">Formulir Data Merchant</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijh-o3borb-041\">Excel docs that contain merchant detail information</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijh-h22sdn-042\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/3/d/1qoHTTaoEPLSuz4AUopojXjpm4UUSkikDLw_DPT3Tlp0/edit\"><u>Template Data Merchant</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijh-hq5qoe-043\">Formulir SubComp</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijh-lty0be-044\">Excel docs that contain merchant subcompany code and business name</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2iji-3smyx7-045\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1eBNxhWD6mp82GHmR72C4mNQqmgELVjTF/edit?usp=share_link&amp;ouid=108011016414156784006&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true\"><u>Template SubComp</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2iji-6gmub0-046\">Website Requirement</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2iji-n60ldr-047\">Guideline for website that ready to submit by merchants, for MO to check and submit to BCA </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2iji-xkbabi-048\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/u/0/d/1yQMBagDfdR9thsuYvw0LfZgMToJM0MA9HuWNeCzT3OI/edit\"><u>Website Requirements for BCA Activation</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2iji-x8286y-049\">Share Drive</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijj-xcbzz1-050\">Platform we use to share merchant’s legal document with BCA </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijj-2w494s-051\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/u/3/folders/0ABDTzoRklKkSUk9PVA\"><u>Share Drive</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijj-x1a9rj-052\">SOP / requirement from BCA [updated 19 Oct 24]</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijj-rbp1bv-053\">SOP / guideline from BCA to apply BCA VA Aggregator</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijj-zsn13z-054\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1AXMt0CRjyDPJ37MCSX8il6mMdJhgtk4F/view?usp=drive_link\"><u>SOP</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijk-l91o0o-055\">Checklist Biller VA Aggregator – FDS</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijk-cgi2u6-056\">FDS checklist with each merchant information</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijk-ptjdiv-057\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1j0IBJMqZ5RM1eSHNeokknOHMZTu8eJdg/edit?usp=drive_link&amp;ouid=108011016414156784006&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true\"><u>template</u></a></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijk-yj1yh6-058\"><a id=\"_7y1u2s87pl3h\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijk-ai8g2h-059\"><a id=\"_41j1s840wsz0\" display=\"false\"></a>Eligibility</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijk-ytzr4l-060\"><strong>Entity Type</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijl-hcfv6b-061\"><strong>Can Apply?</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijl-cautcl-062\">Indonesian Entity (PT/CV/Yayasan)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijl-76e665-063\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijl-lrpkbl-064\">Indonesian Entity (Perseroan perorangan/PP)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijl-cdmxm2-065\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijl-m2dfxl-066\">Indonesian Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijl-mzoqq8-067\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijm-9m5m1k-068\">Foreign Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijm-xa6hnt-069\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijm-yu81lh-070\">Foreign Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijm-gd97u5-071\">❌</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijm-dgfgbx-072\"><a id=\"_ua1gk41r86em\" display=\"false\"></a>Industry Restriction</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijm-1q95si-073\"><em>*) notes: there were some exceptions made if sales are really pushing for this. MO will to coordinate with partnership for partnerships to negotiate with partner.</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijm-zvpyv5-074\"><em>More detail here : </em><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YK7-mYg21fVd4b07pWFzg40yKUBBZWy9/edit#heading=h.327k0rog1nqe\"><em><u>SOP Biller Aggregator (update 26 April 2024).docx</u></em></a></p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijn-96u6qg-075\"><strong>Industry</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijn-we3qlk-076\"><strong>List of Business</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"5\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijn-cotsnw-077\">Pornographic/adult services/night club</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijn-q0k61n-078\">Sale of dangerous products/services, i.e. weaponry, illegal drugs, and narcotics</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijn-1mmgtk-079\">Gambling</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijo-91uobc-080\">Sale of fake/imitated goods in which breaches the intellectual/property rights</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijo-sblpv4-081\">Merchants that indicated/suspected as platform offering illegal cash-out (gesek tunai/gestun)</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijo-fm0z26-082\">Jasa Titip</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"6\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijo-s3ngkz-083\">Financial institutions</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijo-5f96c3-084\">Banks and Remittance</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijo-o88tf7-085\">Peer to Peer lending without license/not registered in Otoritas Jasa Keuangan (OJK)</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijo-cyum68-086\">Payment Gateway or business that can potentially act as an aggregator</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijo-r6nt4h-087\">Merchants classified as Financial Tech or Digital Finance companies without Bank Indonesia license</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijp-tlgp4r-088\">Cryptocurrency</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijp-thytnn-089\">Merchants classified as Financial Tech companies without license/not registered in OJK</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"3\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijp-ctwleh-090\">Non-financial businesses that require licensing</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijp-qiogvw-091\">Sale of alcohol/liquor/booze without license</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijp-q09hld-092\">Sale of living creatures without license i.e breeder, kennel, adoption center</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijp-98kdzc-093\">Business which product/services is yet to be licensed by authorities</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijp-fptf39-094\"><a id=\"_ky35ev5ldil1\" display=\"false\"></a></h3><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijp-mz39ik-095\"><a id=\"_nx8hj42ng5q6\" display=\"false\"></a>Xendit company code </h2><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijp-8d2rqi-096\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijp-maa9bx-097\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-gz8wky-521\">Fixed Bill : 38165</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijq-lhqd3i-098\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-edc6nt-522\">No Bill : 38166</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijq-xpjjv4-099\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-6zovjs-523\">Variable Bill : 38167</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijq-9gozai-100\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-j8nttu-524\">Foreign merchant onboarding subject to partnership approval : 20783</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijq-w9pjm4-101\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-5z9i7r-525\">Exceptional merchant under <strong>APERD only : </strong>15168</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijq-yin12f-102\"><a id=\"_6c0oxkffxx60\" display=\"false\"></a>Merchant Requirements </h2><p data-block-id=\"mmkal1n8-nqzqog-583\">Below are the requirements that merchant has to submit for BCA VA application request:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mmkanm43-50i63u-585\" start=\"1\" data-list-format=\"decimal\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkanm43-n6np26-586\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-d3g12c-526\"><strong>Legal Document </strong></p></li></ol><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-j8enjf-105\" data-list-format=\"disc\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-karhsv-106\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-d3g12c-526\">E-KTP dan NPWP Direktur</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-ymhxbm-108\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-yjdnj4-528\">NPWP PT</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-0iir8l-109\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-abt3bd-529\">SIUP/Izin Usaha</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-jfypnk-110\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-v8nbfl-530\"> TDP/NIB</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-rcu9b5-111\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-mhkjtd-531\">SK Domisili/Izin Lokasi</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-nwnrd4-112\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-n5n26f-532\">Akta dan SK Menkumham Pendirian</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-ojfkx5-113\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-0ddrk9-533\">Akta dan SK Menkumham Perubahan</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-u5qc7e-114\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-sth5e6-534\">Capture web/ flow transaksi / Flow Dummy (needed for merchant with staging website)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-gkkt4g-115\"><br type=\"inline\"><strong>Additional info : </strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-737fuh-117\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-dxqnu8-118\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqt-26gg5h-535\">Lama usaha bisnis </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-keb7jd-119\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqu-rxfg23-536\">Lokasi cabang  pembukaan rekening BCA</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-c9w43f-120\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqu-okkduu-537\">Harga barang/jasa terendah</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijr-9m2eqx-121\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqu-ykhno1-538\">Harga barang/jasa tertinggi</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-wlzput-122\"><strong>2.  Website</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-ylgloq-123\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-88rtcu-124\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqu-ciqx8g-539\">Not Social Media and Micro-Ecommerce and e-commerce</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-88rtcu-124\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqu-ciqx8g-539\">Website must be active and fully running <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/u/0/d/1yQMBagDfdR9thsuYvw0LfZgMToJM0MA9HuWNeCzT3OI/edit\"><u>see above</u></a> guidelines , i.e:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-ylgloq-123\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-jgcsfa-128\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqu-sdrzsb-541\">Link is accessible</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-js897t-129\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqu-x6m6j8-542\">Show product/ service</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-kpp4ir-130\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqu-fu9iu2-543\">Price in IDR</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-wmtm5c-131\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqu-0iimyv-544\">Not a template or “coming soon” website</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-zbzk16-132\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqu-0k4mc3-545\">Must have checkout page</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-06b2u1-133\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqu-mvrtt8-546\">Must have T&amp;C, Privacy Policy, and Refund Policy</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-06b2u1-133\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkampll-pso1lk-584\">Apps is listed in PlayStore / AppStore</p></li></ul><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-jngstw-136\"><a id=\"_qfsyelx4kgod\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-yovlyi-137\"><a id=\"_ujkex4eg0uw0\" display=\"false\"></a>SLA</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-6b5cua-138\">BCA VA Direct Aggregator activated in 5-7 working days from the date merchant submits complete requirements to MO</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-yjlaji-139\"><a id=\"_r0miqi6pvfyc\" display=\"false\"></a>Onboarding Flow</h2><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-ocy8w4-140\"><a id=\"_qn0mmtfunx4k\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-6r9eh4-141\">Category</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-gwpocu-142\">Steps</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijs-bidwxb-143\">Action</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijt-r4sfal-144\">Process Owner</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijt-oec757-145\">Merchant applies for BCA VA</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijt-pp9cqe-146\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijt-r5mr35-147\">Merchant submit application via Dashboard for BCA VA Direct<br type=\"inline\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijt-zjy1gl-149\">Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"4\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijt-w5t378-150\">MO Process Merchant’s Application</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijt-jix3zs-151\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijt-mtfj3l-152\">MO will be able to see merchants who already applied on Admin Dashboard &gt; Channel Activation &gt; BCA VA DIrect</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijt-axb8br-153\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-xs9wx1-154\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-va-direct-image-bkm37lvv.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"4\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-ylehhz-155\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-bnicnx-156\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-3i1h6n-157\">MO process the application by checking merchant’s details: <br type=\"inline\">The maximum of merchant name / brand name is 18 Characters</p><ol data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-zlo00n-159\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-m7o7ex-160\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-qi4kyo-548\">“Nama Perusahaan” must be PT/CV/Yayasan name instead of brand name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-thanw3-161\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-mqxejf-549\">Fulfill the website requirements</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-sdvi8n-162\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-sydo3e-550\">Make sure the BCA account number is under entity name and match with the legal docs. </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-sfz1j9-163\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-243a77-551\">Make sure that all legal documents are completed. </p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-lzifah-164\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-4qgf54-165\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-va-direct-image-irh4wy40.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-e4xuem-166\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2iju-1l4d86-167\">If merchants information did not pass, MO will use this <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NBuwm4jWCmUt3COEdLoOyaHLOGHS-I3rmuI690wKoLw/edit#gid=1546336929\"><u>sheet</u></a> to notify merchants and complete the missing requirements, MO need to  update in this <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1VnEG-H3FO9p9bYTJM-pcp7nmmpIvebpdwsrB5Mepdnc/edit#gid=0\"><u>Tracker</u></a> </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-88r98c-168\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-66qozf-169\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-va-direct-image-5lwy0ll9.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"><br type=\"inline\">*<em>) Email will be sent automatically through Zapier</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-wr8vfy-172\">How to fill the sheet : </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-dz3sls-173\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-v70kny-174\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-rgtzi8-552\">Merchant name : fill with merchant business/legal name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-cl7z2k-175\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-oivpjf-553\">Merchant business email : fill with merchant’s email</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-1xht2k-176\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-yzp2qq-554\">CC alternatif email merchant : fill with merchant’s other email (if any)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-pgry2w-177\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-7q7n9t-555\">CC sales : fill with Xendit sales PIC</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-9t5fuh-178\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-uxani2-556\">CC 1 : fill with email (can be Xendit’s/merchant’s)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-2yozgl-179\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-x44s5n-557\">Details : fill by choosing the dropdown list based on missing requirements. </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-naxwo6-180\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-k9da8m-558\">Message : just leave it (auto generate when choosing details). </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-iyqbl2-181\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqw-31n8cw-559\">Sent email? : fill with ✔ if the data filled are correct. <br type=\"inline\"></p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-c5bo3l-183\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-nwlguc-184\">Once all requirements are completed, MO need to export sheet by clicking <strong>Download XLSX </strong><br type=\"inline\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijv-poullx-187\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-va-direct-image-y5dd02hi.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqx-0oxny7-560\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijw-u8m6qe-188\">6</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijw-uuto9l-189\">Once the sheet is exported, MO need to copy the data and paste it to these form <br type=\"inline\">A. <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1qoHTTaoEPLSuz4AUopojXjpm4UUSkikDLw_DPT3Tlp0/edit#gid=1463994713\"><u>Template Data Merchant</u></a></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijw-1zf924-191\">B. <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1TjyK22adtOnHrwDqvYsde0IxUvw6ucppx3Sgsm-_0Ow/edit#gid=1978646106\"><u>Template Subcomp</u></a><br type=\"inline\">For the Subcomp template MO only needs to change the highlight yellow column. <br type=\"inline\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijx-yckbdq-196\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-va-direct-image-vz3fskle.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijx-ys0u5u-197\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijx-446xs9-198\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqx-3x5hhj-561\">Exceptional for merchant with business  <strong>Agen Penjual Efek Reksa Dana ( APERD )</strong> under OJK<br type=\"inline\">Please change the : <strong>KODE PERUSAHAAN</strong> on Template subcomp to : <strong>15168</strong></p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqx-j7xa46-562\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqx-1ojo0y-563\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijx-64ssew-200\">7</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijx-ndr9qk-201\">Legal document already downloaded and stored in share <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0ABDTzoRklKkSUk9PVA\"><u>Drive</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqy-byjfp6-564\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqy-eht4uz-565\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijy-8tc1gl-202\">8 </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijy-75tscm-203\">Next step is MO to email to BCA with this template: <br type=\"inline\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijy-92l56o-205\"><em>To: </em><a><em><u>cashmanagement_impl@bca.co.id</u></em></a><em> </em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijy-pr322d-206\"><em>Cc: &lt;</em><a><em><u>merchantops@xendit.co</u></em></a><em>&gt; , anggis@xendit.co</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijy-e0wnkp-207\"><em><br type=\"inline\">Subject: [merchantops] Pengajuan VA Aggregator Xendit</em><strong><em> [Date of Submission]</em></strong><em><br type=\"inline\"><br type=\"inline\">Dear Tim BCA,</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijy-mjl24r-208\"><em>Berikut terlampir pengajuan pendaftaran SubComp Biller Aggregator Xendit pada </em><strong><em>[Date of Submission]</em></strong><em>. Total terdapat </em><strong><em>[Number of merchant]</em></strong><em> merchant :</em></p><ol data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijy-b4yrc6-209\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijy-jenjm3-210\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqy-9zzich-566\"><strong><em>[Subcompany code] - [Product Name] </em></strong></p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijz-wugsh2-211\"><em>Berikut link gdrive legal docs merchant dan additional info mengenai web/app dapat dilihat di </em><strong><em>[link gdrive]</em></strong><em> Xendit</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijz-1bhd1e-212\"><em>Mohon untuk dapat diproses dan didaftarkan. Apabila terdapat kekurangan informasi maupun dokumen harap menghubungi kami kembali.</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijz-s0tsd2-213\"><em>Atas kerjasamanya kami ucapkan terima kasih.</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijz-uvh970-214\"><br type=\"inline\">• Exceptional merchant <strong>APERD please send the email to : </strong><br type=\"inline\"><em>cashmanagement_impl@bca.co.id<br type=\"inline\">cc: partnerships@xendit.co </em><a><em><u>riskayanti_kusnadi@bca.co.id</u></em></a></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ijz-3itb3o-217\"><br type=\"inline\">Attach the <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1qoHTTaoEPLSuz4AUopojXjpm4UUSkikDLw_DPT3Tlp0/edit#gid=1463994713\"><u>Template Data Merchant</u></a> and <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1TjyK22adtOnHrwDqvYsde0IxUvw6ucppx3Sgsm-_0Ow/edit#gid=1978646106\"><u>Template Subcomp</u></a> file inside the body of email, also Gdrive link. </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqy-t5fotr-567\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqy-9tsx45-568\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik0-aak982-219\">9</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik0-101xv3-220\">BCA will give feedback around 3-5 days. </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik0-ma1dsb-221\">Below are the example of BCA feedback</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik0-tp6b3p-222\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik0-9bs0fm-223\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-va-direct-image-1sj02dnr.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqz-uly7d9-569\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik0-q8yhx2-224\">BCA VA aggregator activation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik0-0x3xeg-225\">1.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik0-m40qpd-226\">Click Activate Merchants button</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik0-81re2s-227\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik0-1ffpw2-228\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-va-direct-image-vy7tjeqn.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik1-f2m5df-229\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkajlqz-5drxxr-570\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik1-mikhkz-230\">2.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp2ik1-ww6tj2-231\">Choose the date of merchant submission time that already got 